winpodx (0.1.2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * CI: obs-publish and debs-publish now trigger on tag push, not release:published,
    to bypass GitHub's recursive-workflow guard on GITHUB_TOKEN-created releases.
  * Packaging: RPM spec globs the dist-info directory in %files to tolerate
    pyproject.toml / git tag version drift between release bumps.

 -- Kim DaeHyun <kernalix7@kodenet.io>  Tue, 21 Apr 2026 12:00:00 +0900

winpodx (0.1.1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Packaging: drop debtransform from OBS _service; .deb built by GitHub Actions.
  * Packaging: RPM spec uses python313 on Leap 16.0 / Tumbleweed.
  * CI: check-windows-updates opens an Issue instead of a pull request.
  * Docs: install instructions cover openSUSE / Fedora / Debian / Ubuntu prebuilt packages.

 -- Kim DaeHyun <kernalix7@kodenet.io>  Tue, 21 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0900

winpodx (0.1.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.

